name: JusticeLeagueOrigins
0:
”Alexa, open Justice League: Origins.”
”Alexa, ask Justice League: Origins to play Jim Lee's commentary.”
”Alexa, start over.”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: justice league origins
des: Hear Jim Lee share EXCLUSIVE commentary around his experiences and thought processes while drawing Justice League Vol 1 – a critical new origin story in the DC Universe, and an inspiration for the Fall 2017 Justice League movie. Known for his incredibly detailed and dynamic artistic style, Lee is one of the most revered and respected artists in American comics, and currently Co-Publisher of DC Entertainment.
